	blindly pass RUN-MODE,IMAGE,DRAWABLE to LIGMA_PLUGIN procedures but
	look at their parameters and pass them either RUN-MODE, or
	RUN-MODE,IMAGE, or RUN-MODE,IMAGE,DRAWABLE.

